values: Well, its been a long time since i have wrttien in this thing and alot of things have happened, I started Marshall and EMT-B  class and they are going good im  just loaded down with alot of work. I start my new job this friday at CHH, it will be alot better than big sandy. The girlfriend situation is still the same as usuall nothing, who cares anyways. Well i think im gonna go to bed later

Me and Dane are sittn here  at his house being bored. We havent done anything but we did watch unfaithful which is greaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaat! But anyways i got off this morning at 8 and i slept all day since i had to work a 24 and it wasnt to bad. I start school monday which is kinda a bummer but im still ready for something new. Well im outta here later.

Well it been awhile since i have wrote in this thing. Its been bust lately i worked squad last night we werent busy which is a good thing. I put my 2 weeks in a t big sandy wooohooo ive been there for the past 2 years and im ready to get out of that place and on to something better. Im gonna miss some of the guys there, They were good to work with and made it fun somtimes. Well im bored im gonna go find somthing to get into later

Well i just got home from work which wasnt a bad day actually. I have to be at the station at 8 tomorrow and i wont get off until wed morning at 8 so its gonna be a long day but i can sleep atleast. But i really need to rest up cause i have a golf tournament thrursday at grayson at 8 so i really would like to play well so maybe i should get off here and get some rest as joe said . Later

Well its been a night let me tell you its 3 in the morning and i'm just getting home. Ive been up since 6 and i need some sleep. Well i worked all stinking day and then came home and me and my friend calhoun went out for me to meet this girl he wanted me to meet. She was kool but i don't think that there would be anything there i dunno i just really get aggravated with the whole girl situation it seems like the ones i actually want or have feelings are out of reach. Ive had allot of things on my mind lately and some things have happened that bring back allot of things which makes me think which is a bad thing cause i cant get things off of my mind when i do. Well im outta here later

WoW! This is my first entry in this thing, Ive seen allot of my friends have these things so i figured what they hey! Well its been kind of a slow day for some reason me and Burns went to Huntington earlier today for me to go to ronks for me to get some uniform stuff for work at the station. Well then me and Howard, Dane, Russo, and laura went and seen the village. Well the movie sucks don't go and see it. Well i'm outta here i gotta be at work tomorrow at 8 later.
